Would they buy a home in Agura Hills, a cute ranch home for $2.3 million?

24:29.000 --> 24:34.000
When they bailed out me and the incumbents three years ago,

24:34.000 --> 24:36.000
all they were doing was robbing opportunity from young people.

24:36.000 --> 24:40.000
When you bail out the boomer who owns a restaurant,

24:40.000 --> 24:44.000
