25:14.000 --> 25:18.000
and the kind of denigration of our public discourse

25:18.000 --> 25:25.000
and the increase in distrust in institutions matched with the lack of opportunity

25:25.000 --> 25:30.000
and everything that you just outlined, like, does America survive this?

