Look, we have a tendency to believe that me and my colleagues

30:38.000 --> 30:40.000
are somehow more noble than the rest of the population,

30:40.000 --> 30:42.000
and we sit around with our labradors

30:42.000 --> 30:44.000
and our corduroy vests watching PBS

30:44.000 --> 30:46.000
thinking about how to make the world a better place.

