And COVID provided the perfect opportunity

32:40.000 --> 32:43.000
to reevaluate what you just shared

32:43.000 --> 32:47.000
and create a situation through online education

32:47.000 --> 32:50.000
to broaden the aperture and make it accessible

32:50.000 --> 32:51.000
to so many more people.

32:51.000 --> 32:53.000
And we all know what happened.

32:53.000 --> 32:54.000
That didn't happen.

32:54.000 --> 32:55.000
It didn't.

32:55.000 --> 32:56.000
Yeah.

32:56.000 --> 32:58.000
